{"tid":1286681,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"肚瀉一問","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T15:54:34.000Z","uid":218129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a78a019f5c3be73dce0a1308bfd05c0dd2beee7","tid":1286681,"uid":218129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"星期一晚發燒 去左2次廁所 （水狀）<br />\n<br />\n星期二 （早上退左燒）<br />\n去左睇醫生 食左感冒藥同退燒 但夜晚又發燒<br />\n去左幾次廁所 （水狀）<br />\n<br />\n星期三 退左燒 但幾頭痛 同埋痾到仆街<br />\n平均3～4h去一次廁所 都係水狀<br />\n<br />\n星期四去左覆診 醫生打左針同俾左消炎藥<br />\n醫生話頸淋巴腫哂<br />\n靜係痾左兩次 睇醫生之前一次 夜晚一次<br />\n<br />\n今日早上又痾左次 都係水狀 <br />\n總括 發燒（期間有發冷同脈搏加快）流鼻血（因為唔肯定幾時流 但肯定有）肚痾..<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生話如果繼續痾就係要照超聲波"},{"pid":"98b1573198897fcb28d37022d61c08280eeb33c2","tid":1286681,"uid":218129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121bd7066d28342102bf8e99c98bca9da6db90cd","tid":1286681,"uid":69140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:00:18.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"480d264c5e4f810726071b56f79fc74fdc12f5a5","tid":1286681,"uid":218129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaa2937e80723c0d0c996d1e433147e744783d36","tid":1286681,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔問埋醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459f08d00ae75250545c6a607b8faa068350153e","tid":1286681,"uid":240671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"係咪感冒菌入腸呀"},{"pid":"5d2110dab1da11df4224a30eb9f3eab88ef780a7","tid":1286681,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"係咪地捫西梅汁當水飲"},{"pid":"2690d2203f66e6314014e7a6f78c715c5773138d","tid":1